articles.title: Moschino Creative Director Davide Renne Dies at 46 - WWD
articles.description: The designer, hailing from Gucci, was named to the role last month and started in his new post on Nov. 1
articles.content:
Updated Nov. 10 2:38 p.m. EST
MILAN — The Milan fashion scene was shaken Friday by the news that Davide Renne, newly named creative director of Moschino, has died of undisclosed causes at 46.
